These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, architect
1. the mechanic is on the right of the architect##1
2. the architect is not to the right of the architect##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Job   | architect | mechanic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
City: boston, liverpool
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to boston is not to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| City   | liverpool | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, sports
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
3. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person watching scientific movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | sports |

 #################################

 
